dreams.dream: Jag drömmer i drömmen. Jag är hela tiden medveten om att barnen gått tidigare för att gå till skolannoch att jag somnat om. Men u drömmen somnar jag om på landet. Mamma och pappa är hemma och jag gör deras röster i bakgrunden. Jag ligger i våningssängen längst ned och sover. Och vaknar och somnar om. Men sen vaknar jag och stiger upp och så kan jag fälla ihop sängen till en fällsäng. Jag hinner fundera kring hur jag ska göra med katten eftersom barnen kommer hem på eftermiddagen och katten är kvar i stan. Sen något om någon match på tv där kommmentstlrn plötsligt dyker upp i bild och en kvinnlig datorröst refererar obegripligt. Sen vaknar jag igen i drömmen fast i våningssängen och inser att jag bara har drömt. Sedan måste jag alltså vakna en gång till och inse att jag varken sover i våningssäng eller på Ingarö och alltså inte behöver tänka på katten. Det är onsdag och klockan är 10:14 och jag har äntligen fått sova ut.
dreams.interpretation: Based on the dream, it seems that the dreamer may be experiencing some level of stress or anxiety in their daily life. The dream reflects a need for rest, relaxation, and escape from the routine of everyday life. The dreamer may also be feeling overwhelmed with responsibilities such as taking care of the children and worrying about the cat. The dream may be a manifestation of the dreamer's desire for a break or a diversion from their current situation. Additionally, the dream may indicate a need for the dreamer to confront their fears or concerns, represented by the unclear commentary on the TV, and to find peace and clarity within themselves.

dreams.dream: I dreamd I was riding a big beautiful black horse. It was a very good horse, but I kept loosing control over it because the reins was old and tourn. I tried to water the horse in the stable but it was hard. I tied up the horse because other wise it was disobidient in the padock. I felt  I was to far away froom him when I climbed a hill to watch the view, there where trees where cut down so I could see the landskape.
dreams.interpretation:
Riding a black horse in your dream represents your desire to take control over your life. However, you seem to be facing obstacles that prevent you from fully controlling the situation as the reins are old and torn. This could suggest that you need to update or improve certain aspects of your life that are holding you back.

The difficulty in watering the horse may symbolize a struggle to meet your emotional or physical needs. Tying up the horse indicates a need for self-discipline to prevent self-sabotage in certain areas of your life.

The feeling of being too far away from the horse may represent a sense of detachment or disconnection from a certain aspect of yourself. The hill in the dream represents a higher perspective that allows you to see things more clearly, but the cut-down trees suggest that something valuable has been lost or sacrificed.

Overall, this dream suggests that you need to take control over certain aspects of your life and be more disciplined, but you should also pay attention to your emotional and physical needs and try to reconnect with important aspects of yourself that may have been lost.
dreams.title: Lost Reigns: Taming the Untamed Black Stallion in a Cut Down Landscape

dreams.dream:
Var utomlands med min partner då någon berättade det fanns en orörd sjunken yacht utanför en ö full med dyra exklusiva saker ombord. 
Personen erbjöd sig följa oss, och en vän som var med på resan, till vraket.
Väl där var vattnet så klart och skeppet låg så grunt att vi från båten vi åkt på klart kunde se alla dyra föremål som låg utspridda på botten. 
Tyvärr kunde man inte gå ner då det fanns massor av aggresiva hajar vilket var orsaken till att det var orört. 
Tillbaka på hotellet, besviken, såg jag från balkongen en ingång  från en trappa ner till skeppet. Jag ropade till mitt sällskap vad jag sett samtidigt som jag sprang dit. 
Väl framme och jag går ner till fartyget kommer en kvinnlig försäljare fram och på grekiska hälsar mig välkommen. Inser då skeppet bara är en exklusiv affär och att allt var till salu för enorma summor.
Besviken gick jag upp för att möta mitt sällskap och berätta hur det låg till..
dreams.interpretation: This dream may suggest a desire for excitement and adventure, as well as the potential for indulging in luxury or extravagance. The yacht represents an opportunity to explore something new and exciting, while the presence of expensive items on board may be indicative of a desire for wealth and material possessions. The aggressive sharks could represent obstacles or fears that may be preventing you from enjoying the adventure. The appearance of a saleswoman and the discovery that the yacht was actually a shop suggests that perhaps you are searching for fulfillment and satisfaction in material objects, rather than experiencing true adventure and thrill. The disappointment at the end of the dream may indicate a realisation that material possessions cannot provide true happiness or fulfillment.

dreams.dream: Was in France on a study visit. Went down far underground where there was a nursing home. Be afraid as I have a phobia of tight spaces. Met there a woman who lived there. Hug her and were very happy to see each other, even though I had never seen or met her before. Unfortunately she spoke French so we tried to make ourselves understood with the help of my bad school French. Was very frustrating as it felt like we had a lot to say to each other but that never came out.
dreams.interpretation: This dream could represent unresolved emotions or feelings that you have towards someone whom you have not seen or connected with in a long time. This could also symbolize a fear of the unknown or a fear of intimacy. The nursing home could represent a feeling of being trapped or confined in a situation or in a relationship. Your inability to fully communicate with the woman could signify a lack of connection or understanding in a particular aspect of your life. Perhaps, this dream is encouraging you to be more open and communicative about your thoughts and feelings, and to try to overcome any fears or obstacles that may be hindering your ability to form deeper connections with others.
dreams.title: Lost in Translation: A Phobic Encounter in an Underground Nursing Home
